Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是溫泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺以前好像來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡好像發生過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過來來去去都是一樣的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有點厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾 我們可不是在遊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這附近好像有溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}溫泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就類似於自然的浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是受地熱加溫的地下水噴薄而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形成一定大小後的狀態對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾 剛才說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們可不是在遊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但稍微放鬆一下應該可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是稍作放鬆的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繞個道也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}適當的休息也是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大叔你也開車那麼久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瑟里卡也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是所謂的溫泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好大一個浴場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水溫真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天空也格外美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是所謂的溫泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還是第一次親眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說泡溫泉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「真舒適啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「活過來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「這簡直是人間天堂」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該這樣說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是大叔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大叔你感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好想快點去泡溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過真沒想到這種地方竟然有溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過這種時候沒有實體還真叫人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說疤面姐姐的胸部真大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我生來就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以也沒怎麼在意過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身材又好 皮膚也好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說對吧 蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒂伊的胸部也好大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明沒比我大幾歲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手感也是不錯的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或許
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這本應該是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為沒有實體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以只有我能摸到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我長大以後胸部也會像疤面和蒂伊這麼大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真舒適啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大叔你一把年紀了身體還很健壯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可不會輸給年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你應該再多加鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經停止成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個世界是虛假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們身在被封鎖的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甚至還不知道自己被封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒有發瘋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這個空間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}任何東西只要受到不可恢復的損害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都會被重置為初期設定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回到最初那一無所知的和平狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我討厭這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我討厭他們被封鎖在這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我絕對不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就和他們一同歡笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直到解放的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住手 艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有一個人我也要堅持到底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}星期一 神創造了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}星期二 神劃分了條理和混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}星期三 神調整了細微的數值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}星期四 神允許了時間的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}星期五 神看盡了世界每一個角落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}星期六 神休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接著神在星期天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就是漢普尼·韓伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個擁有不死之身的男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喲 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前你好像是想讓我去一趟歐斯提亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們之前有見過面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這證明我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許你也請了神那個混蛋幫你實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這對我們彼此來說都很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是為了自己的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算一切會得以重置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣做都是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至今所犯下的罪孽已不可磨滅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想必我的愚蠢是死都治不好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有成為怪物的覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然看似有很多原委
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我似乎幫不上忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只願相信自己親眼所見的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕要訴諸暴力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是那麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 你太客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差不多該回車裡了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟晚上很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:13:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到頭來你還是得以一死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在你來看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我無疑是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一再為不老不死所惑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經沒有必要去尋找了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定會再回來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟常言道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愚蠢是死都治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一開始沒有任何人察覺到那一天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早上一如既往地上學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}報紙上也沒作出任何報導
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既無天崩 也無地裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也沒有神的宣告
